caso isso ajude na escolha.

528
00:27:42,824 --> 00:27:44,024
Tchau, Michelle.

529
00:27:44,025 --> 00:27:46,661
- Tchau.
- Tchau, insista!

530
00:27:51,751 --> 00:27:54,142
